        "data": "<h1 id=\"01H8066N1X71BMWR8KPQVMTM4A\" class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-left\">Service Updates for Liferay Cloud</h1>\n<p>The services update for 03/26/2024 is a minor update for<strong> Backup</strong>,<strong> Database, </strong>and patch update for<strong> web server </strong>service.</p>\n<h2 id=\"01H8066N1X678XQSM8P38E9Q5Z\">DXP Cloud Stack - 03/26/2024 </h2>\n<table class=\"table table-autofit table-list table-nowrap\" style=\"width: 625px; float: left; height: 250px;\">\n<thead>\n<tr style=\"height: 62px;\">\n<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\" style=\"width: 84.8047px; height: 62px; background-color: #969996;\"><strong>Service Name</strong></td>\n<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\" style=\"width: 69.4688px; height: 62px; background-color: #969996;\"><strong>Previous Release</strong></td>\n<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\" style=\"width: 63.1641px; height: 62px; background-color: #969996;\"><strong>Current Release</strong></td>\n<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\" style=\"width: 362.562px; height: 62px; background-color: #969996;\"><strong>Docker Images</strong></td>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody valign=\"top\">\n<tr style=\"height: 48px;\">\n<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\" style=\"width: 84.8047px; text-align: left; vertical-align: top; height: 10px; background-color: #f7f8f9;\">\n<p class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\"><strong>Backup</strong></p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\" style=\"width: 69.4688px; text-align: left; vertical-align: top; height: 10px; background-color: #f7f8f9;\">\n<p class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\">5.14.1</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\" style=\"width: 63.1641px; text-align: left; vertical-align: top; height: 10px; background-color: #f7f8f9;\">\n<p class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\"><strong>5.15.0</strong></p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\" style=\"width: 362.562px; text-align: left; vertical-align: top; height: 10px; background-color: #f7f8f9;\">\n<p class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\"><strong>liferaycloud/backup:5.15.0</strong></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 36px;\">\n<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\" style=\"width: 84.8047px; vertical-align: top; height: 28px;\">\n<p class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\">CI</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\" style=\"width: 69.4688px; vertical-align: top; height: 28px;\">\n<p class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\">5.2.4</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\" style=\"width: 63.1641px; vertical-align: top; height: 28px;\">\n<p class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\">5.2.5</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\" style=\"width: 362.562px; vertical-align: top; height: 28px;\">\n<p class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\">liferaycloud/jenkins:2.356-jdk8-5.2.5</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 41.2222px;\">\n<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\" style=\"width: 84.8047px; vertical-align: top; height: 28px; background-color: #f7f8f9;\">\n<p class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\"><strong>Database</strong></p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\" style=\"width: 69.4688px; vertical-align: top; height: 28px; background-color: #f7f8f9;\">\n<p class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\">5.3.0</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\" style=\"width: 63.1641px; vertical-align: top; height: 28px; background-color: #f7f8f9;\">\n<p class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\"><strong>5.4.0</strong></p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\" style=\"width: 362.562px; vertical-align: top; height: 28px; background-color: #f7f8f9;\">\n<p class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\"><strong>liferaycloud/database:5.4.0</strong></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 36px;\">\n<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\" style=\"width: 84.8047px; vertical-align: top; height: 48px;\">Liferay</td>\n<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\" style=\"width: 69.4688px; vertical-align: top; height: 48px;\">\n<p class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\">5.4.0</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\" style=\"width: 63.1641px; vertical-align: top; height: 48px;\">\n<p class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\">5.5.0</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\" style=\"width: 362.562px; vertical-align: top; height: 48px;\">\n<p class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\">liferaycloud/liferay-dxp:7.4-5.5.0<br>liferaycloud/liferay-dxp:7.3-5.5.0<br>liferaycloud/liferay-dxp:7.2-5.5.0<br>liferaycloud/liferay-dxp:7.1-5.5.0<br>liferaycloud/liferay-dxp:7.0-5.5.0</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 36px;\">\n<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\" style=\"width: 84.8047px; text-align: left; vertical-align: top; height: 48px;\">\n<p class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\">Search</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\" style=\"width: 69.4688px; text-align: left; vertical-align: top; height: 48px;\">\n<p class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\">5.2.1</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\" style=\"width: 63.1641px; text-align: left; vertical-align: top; height: 48px;\">\n<p class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\">5.3.0</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\" style=\"width: 362.562px; text-align: left; vertical-align: top; height: 48px;\">\n<p class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\">liferaycloud/elasticsearch:8.12.1-5.3.0 liferaycloud/elasticsearch:7.17.18-5.3.0</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 36px;\">\n<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\" style=\"width: 84.8047px; text-align: left; vertical-align: top; height: 26px; background-color: #f7f8f9;\">\n<p class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\"><strong>Webserver</strong></p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\" style=\"width: 69.4688px; text-align: left; vertical-align: top; height: 26px; background-color: #f7f8f9;\">\n<p class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\">5.4.0</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\" style=\"width: 63.1641px; text-align: left; vertical-align: top; height: 26px; background-color: #f7f8f9;\">\n<p class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\"><strong>5.4.1</strong></p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\" style=\"width: 362.562px; text-align: left; vertical-align: top; height: 26px; background-color: #f7f8f9;\">\n<p class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\"><strong>liferaycloud/nginx:1.21.6-5.4.1</strong><br><span style=\"font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;\"></span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<h2 id=\"h_01HHMXJ7P5R5AAYGTJH56HRMTY\"> </h2>\n<h2 id=\"h_01HHMXJ7P5GY0CZ5PS8BF5J5WV\"> </h2>\n<h2 id=\"h_01HHMXJ7P5RVBVJ18S7CYNGTXE\"> </h2>\n<h2 id=\"h_01HHMXJ7P5ZPY1BSN55Y4QYC5H\"> </h2>\n<h2 id=\"h_01HHMXJ7P5P207YSD8QGRVHKHM\"> </h2>\n<h2 id=\"h_01HHMXJ7P5H7X4QGDRNX57R56Z\"> </h2>\n<h2 id=\"h_01HHMXJ7P5WDFZWS3PMJGFEQN6\"> </h2>\n<h2 id=\"h_01HHMXJ7P5816SKC44SZKY7CG6\"> </h2>\n<h2 id=\"h_01HHMXJ7P68NF6JY3S1C4DZ119\"> </h2>\n<h2 id=\"h_01HR82YW7WFKWZYTVAFDVWPT6B\"> </h2>\n<p> </p>\n<h2 id=\"01H8066N1YWTXV16JYNYMDV6F4\">Change Log</h2>\n<table class=\"table table-autofit table-list table-nowrap\" style=\"margin-left: 0px; margin-right: auto; height: 138px; width: 642px;\">\n<thead>\n<tr style=\"height: 62px;\">\n<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\" style=\"background-color: #f7f8f9; width: 98.1641px; height: 62px;\"><strong>Service Name</strong></td>\n<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\" style=\"background-color: #f7f8f9; width: 80.1406px; height: 62px;\"><strong>Service Version</strong></td>\n<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\" style=\"background-color: #f7f8f9; width: 89.1562px; height: 62px;\"><strong>Ticket No.</strong></td>\n<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\" style=\"background-color: #f7f8f9; width: 329.539px; height: 62px;\"><strong>Description</strong></td>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody valign=\"top\">\n<tr style=\"height: 22px;\">\n<td style=\"width: 98.1641px; text-align: left; vertical-align: top; height: 10px;\">\n<p class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\"><strong> Backup</strong></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 80.1406px; text-align: left; vertical-align: top; height: 10px;\">\n<p class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\"><strong> 5.15.0</strong></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 89.1562px; vertical-align: top; height: 10px;\"><a href=\"https://liferay.atlassian.net/browse/LCD-33138\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">LCD-33138</a></td>\n<td style=\"width: 329.539px; text-align: left; vertical-align: top; height: 10px;\">Add basic support for PostgresSQL*</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 22px;\">\n<td style=\"width: 98.1641px; text-align: left; vertical-align: top; height: 22px;\">\n<p class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\"><strong>Database </strong></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 80.1406px; text-align: left; vertical-align: top; height: 22px;\">\n<p class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\"><strong> 5.4.0</strong></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 89.1562px; vertical-align: top; height: 22px;\"><a href=\"https://liferay.atlassian.net/browse/LCD-33138\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">LCD-33138</a></td>\n<td style=\"width: 329.539px; text-align: left; vertical-align: top; height: 22px;\">Add basic support for PostgresSQL*</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 98.1641px; text-align: left; vertical-align: top;\">\n<p class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\"><strong> </strong></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 80.1406px; text-align: left; vertical-align: top;\">\n<p class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\"><strong> </strong></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 89.1562px; vertical-align: top;\"><a href=\"https://liferay.atlassian.net/browse/LCD-24612\">LCD-24612</a></td>\n<td style=\"width: 329.539px; text-align: left; vertical-align: top;\">Remove HAProxy from database service*</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 98.1641px; text-align: left; vertical-align: top;\">\n<p class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\"><strong> </strong></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 80.1406px; text-align: left; vertical-align: top;\">\n<p class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\"><strong> </strong></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 89.1562px; vertical-align: top;\"><a href=\"https://liferay.atlassian.net/browse/LCD-36147\">LCD-36147</a></td>\n<td style=\"width: 329.539px; text-align: left; vertical-align: top;\">Security: Fix container escape &gt; CVE-2024-21626</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 44px;\">\n<td style=\"width: 98.1641px; text-align: left; vertical-align: top; height: 44px;\">\n<p class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\"><strong> Web server</strong></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 80.1406px; text-align: left; vertical-align: top; height: 44px;\">\n<p class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\"><strong> 5.4.1</strong></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 89.1562px; vertical-align: top; height: 44px;\"><a href=\"https://liferay.atlassian.net/browse/LCD-35350\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">LCD-35350</a></td>\n<td style=\"width: 329.539px; text-align: left; vertical-align: top; height: 44px;\">Security: Fix vulnerability: nginx &gt; master &gt; glib &gt; CVE-2023-29499</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<h2 id=\"h_01HSY4SCCXCBSYA88HPHMNEGQH\"> </h2>\n<h2 id=\"h_01HFQQE47127T9RVN8YK7MKH4R\">Update Instructions</h2>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; color: #2a303e; font-family: ' Source Sans Pro' , ' Source Serif Pro' , -apple-system, ' system-ui' , ' Segoe UI' , Roboto, ' Helvetica Neue' , Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: #0b5fff; text-decoration: none; background-color: transparent;\" href=\"https://liferay.atlassian.net/browse/LCD-33138\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">LCD-33138</a><span> </span>: As part of this release we are just adding basic support for PostgresSQL. In a future release we will release the capability for new projects to be provisioned with PostgreSQL as their dedicated database. This will have no impact to existing customer projects. </p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; color: #2a303e; font-family: ' Source Sans Pro' , ' Source Serif Pro' , -apple-system, ' system-ui' , ' Segoe UI' , Roboto, ' Helvetica Neue' , Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: #0b5fff; text-decoration: none; background-color: transparent;\" href=\"https://liferay.atlassian.net/browse/LCD-24612\">LCD-24612</a><span> </span>: From this release onwards we are removing haproxy from database service. This is an internal feature that was previously used to connect liferay service and the database instance. We have moved away from using Haproxy since this release<span> </span><a class=\"article-list-link\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: #0041be; text-decoration: underline; background-color: transparent;\" href=\"https://support.liferay.com/w/2020-08-11-services-update-2020-33-1\">8/11/2020 Services Update 2020.33.1 (See details about the change in this release note)</a></p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; color: #2a303e; font-family: ' Source Sans Pro' , ' Source Serif Pro' , -apple-system, ' system-ui' , ' Segoe UI' , Roboto, ' Helvetica Neue' , Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><em style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">Since this is not an official customer facing feature, it's safe to remove this. No Customer should be impacted by this. </em></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><strong style=\"font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">Note</strong><span style=\"font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"> : To take advantage of the new features and fixes provided by the 5.x stack of services, you must update your entire stack to the new 5.x images.</span></p>\n<h2 id=\"01H8066N1YDXGGCTPJ2C2XKQWE\">Image Update Instructions</h2>\n<p>The Liferay Cloud image versions needs to be set inside of the &lt;service&gt;/LCP.json file.</p>\n<p>Note, however, that the liferay service uses two image properties. The DXP Cloud image is set in the liferay/LCP.json file, but the liferay/dxp image is set in the gradle.properties. This change was made in order to facilitate easier deployment using the Liferay Cloud CLI.</p>\n<p>liferay/LCP.json file would set the liferaycloud/liferay-dxp image:</p>\n<pre><span>\"image\"</span>:<span>\"liferaycloud/liferay-dxp:7.2-5.0.X\"</span></pre>\n<p>liferay/gradle.properties file would set the liferay/dxp image:</p>\n<pre><span>liferay.workspace.docker.image.liferay</span>=<span>liferay/dxp:7.4-x</span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"></span></pre>\n<p>For all other images, you will just need to update the LCP.json file with the intended image version.</p>\n<p>Once the LCP.json files are updated, commit the changes to your Git repository.</p>\n<pre>git add . &amp;&amp; git commit -m \"Update dxp cloud stack to XXX\"</pre>\n<p>After pushing these changes to the remote repository, a build will be created in Liferay Cloud and it is ready to deploy.</p>"
      },
